Title: Part 9: The Dead Marshes
Text:
I met the creature, Gollum.
He must have been following us.
I don't trust him, but I have no choice.
After all, I need a guide into Mordor and he knows the way.
Our next destination is the Dead Marshes.(x79549 y64 z53913)
And from there toward the road point in North Ithilien.
CompleteText:
Finally, the long journey through this stinking bog is over.

There is a way up that mountain to the east!
I should take a look around.
I'm sure I'll have a better view from there.
